    "name": "黑安娜",
    "steam_appid": 3002400,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《黑安娜》是以英国民间传说为基础，设定在现代虚构世界中的一系列短篇恐怖解谜探索游戏中的第一款。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎来到 Lone Oak 学院</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002400/extras/1efd402cd2caffce786d44a41cbcdabb.poster.avif?t=1761525654\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002400/extras/1efd402cd2caffce786d44a41cbcdabb.webm?t=1761525654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002400/extras/1efd402cd2caffce786d44a41cbcdabb.mp4?t=1761525654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在过去的250年里，传说中有一个致命的幽灵出没于Leicester的Dane Hills地区，人和动物会不时神秘失踪，毫无踪迹。传说讲述了一棵孤零零的橡树，它是这一切事件的中心。随着现代城市的扩张，这个故事逐渐被人遗忘，变成了传说。但如果传闻属实，黑安娜仍潜伏在黑暗中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002400/extras/74b39c9e1401c7eb03fea15fe555e39e.poster.avif?t=1761525654\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002400/extras/74b39c9e1401c7eb03fea15fe555e39e.webm?t=1761525654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002400/extras/74b39c9e1401c7eb03fea15fe555e39e.mp4?t=1761525654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为夜班工作人员，你将在一所刚翻修过的学院中解决众多谜题，穿越被封锁的校园，揭开黑安娜背后的历史。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002400/extras/17295c5d1ac7cb9d942ace256fad0319.poster.avif?t=1761525654\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002400/extras/17295c5d1ac7cb9d942ace256fad0319.webm?t=1761525654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002400/extras/17295c5d1ac7cb9d942ace256fad0319.mp4?t=1761525654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只有揭开真相，你才能逃脱她的掌控，在绝望中寻找失踪的朋友并找到出路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002400/extras/97dd725330485424f72f55e144c8bd6c.poster.avif?t=1761525654\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002400/extras/97dd725330485424f72f55e144c8bd6c.webm?t=1761525654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002400/extras/97dd725330485424f72f55e144c8bd6c.mp4?t=1761525654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于黑安娜的本地传说，这是一款讲述她在莱斯特丹希尔斯地区徘徊数百年的游戏。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏玩法：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在逼真的环境中进行紧张的探索</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >机制：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 第一人称解谜互动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多结局</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分支对话</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自动保存</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设计为在两小时内完成的短暂体验</p></li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 日语, 韩语, 挪威语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 简体中文, 苏格兰语, 威尔士语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
